    "body": "Problem:\r\nUsing cterm=/gui= marked highlights as fully set, preventing fg/bg\r\ncolors from updating on background change.\r\n\r\nSolution:\r\nIntroduce per-attr and per-color sg_set flags so colors can be reset\r\nindependently.\r\n\r\nFix #26603 ",
